== 車票 ==
[[File:Ticket_machine_at_Zurich_Airport_tram_stop_03.jpg|缩略图]]
蘇黎世電車採用[[信用乘车系统|信用乘车系统]]，每個車站都設有售票機，乘客上車前必需確保持有有效車票，上車時沒有閘口核實，但是會有票務員抽樣檢查，如果乘客未能出示有效車票，票務員會發出告票，當場罰款<ref name=vbzatm>{{cite web | url = http://www.stadt-zuerich.ch/content/vbz/en/index/tickets/fare_zone_system.html | title = VBZ - Automatic ticket machine | publisher = City of Zürich | access-date = 2012-05-21 | archive-date = 2013-01-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130124042857/http://www.stadt-zuerich.ch/content/vbz/en/index/tickets/fare_zone_system.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

